{"tha-ap296:0.1":"Therapadana ","tha-ap296:0.2":"Citakapujakavagga ","tha-ap296:0.3":"Saddasannakattheraapadana ","tha-ap296:1.1":"“Anuggatamhi adicce, ","tha-ap296:1.2":"panado vipulo ahu; ","tha-ap296:1.3":"Buddhasetthassa lokamhi, ","tha-ap296:1.4":"patubhavo mahesino. ","tha-ap296:2.1":"Ghosamassosaham tattha, ","tha-ap296:2.2":"na ca passami tam jinam; ","tha-ap296:2.3":"Marananca anuppatto, ","tha-ap296:2.4":"buddhasannamanussarim. ","tha-ap296:3.1":"Catunnavutito kappe, ","tha-ap296:3.2":"yam sannamalabhim tada; ","tha-ap296:3.3":"Duggatim nabhijanami, ","tha-ap296:3.4":"buddhapujayidam phalam. ","tha-ap296:4.1":"Patisambhida catasso, ","tha-ap296:4.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap296:4.3":"katam buddhassa sasanam”. ","tha-ap296:5.1":"Ittham sudam ayasma saddasannako thero ima gathayo abhasitthati. ","tha-ap296:6.1":"Saddasannakattherassapadanam catuttham. "}